node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Uloo - Stay Curious! on July 16, 2021. May be an image of ‎1 person and ‎text that says '‎اماد Build positive energy for your day! Discover the science and practice of Meditation with Laurence Buddha-CEO Quantum Foundation DAILY AT 8 AM (ceT) FROM 19 TO 23 JULY uloo.me/laurence Uloo‎'‎‎.

node.text:
👉 Register for this free challenge on https://uloo.me/laurence.⠀⠀⠀
⏰ We will kick off the challenge on Monday 19 July at 8 AM (CET)⠀⠀
----------------⠀
You heard about meditation, maybe you were told about the multiple benefits of meditation, especially in these difficult times, and maybe you were even asked : "hey, why are you still not meditating?". Or how many times did you come up with an excuse to not meditate ?⠀
⠀
During these 5-day challenge, invest in you! You will finally learn the science and practice of meditation, and also understand how meditation helps you manage stress, become more self-aware, more present, reduce negative thoughts or emotions, boost your energy, gain clarity and new perspectives, become more friendly and happier too. And much more.⠀
⠀
These 5 daily live sessions will help you start your meditation habit, stop making excuses, and encourage you to continue further your journey.⠀
----------------⠀
#groupmeditation #teamchallenge #team #meditation #mindfulness #morning #morningmeditation #meditate #meditatedaily #meditation #mindful #mindfulness #mindfulnessmeditation #manifest #manifestyourdreams

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Uloo - Stay Curious! on April 27, 2021. May be an image of office and text that says 'Linkedin V Linkedln Challenge with Pawel THURSDAY 29 APRIL PM (ceT) uloo.me/pawel Uloo'.

node.text:
Have you heard that LinkedIn is a great tool for finding a new job, B2B sales, developing your reputation, and finding the right talent for your team? Probably you have. ⠀
⠀
But do you know how to actually do these things? Should you post content more often or rather focus on improving your profile? Should you use video and reach out to people you don't know? ⠀
⠀
If you feel confused about how to use LinkedIn effectively, then this challenge is for you!⠀
---------------⠀⠀⠀
👉 Register for this free challenge on http://uloo.me/pawel.⠀⠀
⏰ We will kick off the challenge on Thursday 29 April at 4 PM (CET)⠀
---------------⠀⠀
#linkedin #linkedinchallenge #linkedinclass #onlineclass #learn #workshop
